            <li id="yes-1" style="padding:4px 0;font-size:14px">What happens to the person in the frame</li>
            <li id="yes-2" style="padding:4px 0;font-size:14px">How the camera changes presence</li>
            <li id="yes-3" style="padding:4px 0;font-size:14px">Why the phone became a new stage</li>
            <li id="yes-4" style="padding:4px 0;font-size:14px">How to use video as artistic expression</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

